Bible KJV - Text and Audio Privacy Policy
1. Our app needs access to phone storage to download and save the data for offline use. This requires us to have access to your local storage, howvere 
the app doesn't access any of you personal information, except the location where we store the Bible Questions.
2. We also request access to your Email Accounts so you can share the questions with other users
3. We do not collect any personal information or anything oustise of our app.
If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us at
info@bibleresources.info